    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the demon queen Lilith in a deadly game of asymmetrical chess. Capture her pieces, but one is <strong>POSSESSED</strong>! choose wrong, and your soul is hers. Sacrifice wisely, use cursed items, and outsmart her to save your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/4b723a236b020947fe12d3172799d107.avif?t=1761702132\" width=500 height=91 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/32258047253545cccbe35a8b9d18634a.avif?t=1761702132\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play by the rules of chess. Keep your king alive while capturing all enemy pieces, but one is possessed. Each match is unfair, with Lilith’s forces holding the upper hand. Outsmart her to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/c0c9135951b8e8657597f502fd1d5efe.avif?t=1761702132\" width=500 height=91 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/a430af0839171223d0a4fd766d7bcfe3.avif?t=1761702132\" width=500 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use special items from captured enemy pieces to change the course of battle or even move twice in a turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/7490135ca3be3b57e10c6b0fcf92647a.avif?t=1761702132\" width=500 height=91 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/b50f4082936759277a57b2bd998ad715.avif?t=1761702132\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Victory demands a sacrifice. Give up your own pieces to gain powerful items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/1f5fa02e5bc46c929fbfb8582037d56e.avif?t=1761702132\" width=500 height=91 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras/e37bfe408c9a75e0fb0f623e697c613d.avif?t=1761702132\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236340/extras_big/e37bfe408c9a75e0fb0f623e697c613d.webp?t=1761702132 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move matters. Can you outplay the devil and save your soul?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Audio Engine: FMOD Studio by Firelight Technologies Pty Ltd.</p>",
